You can use this to keep an extra pair of shoes or sandals if you may need them. The back padding and shoulder straps are well ventilated and soft. The bag is designed with reflective branding to keep you safe in the dark. It warns others of your presence and avoids accidents. Fitpack Neo is not only a stylish backpack for college students but also a great travel backpack. Just throw in your clothes and travel essentials and hit the road.
